  "text": "In the injective model structure, cofibrant diagrams are diagrams of cofibrant objects of E, that is (( If we suppose that K is of characteristic zero, then this result can be extended to colored props, i.e. props equiped with a set of colors labeling inputs and outputs of the operations (see [CITATION_1] ).",
